These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Beverage     | sprite    | hot-chocolate   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Hobby      | board-games  | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
House: palace, farmhouse
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| House   | farmhouse    | palace |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| House       | gothic-revival | ranch-style    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, polish
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Music-Genre           | blues | d&b |
| Nationality   | polish    | dutch         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rugby
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, documentary
1. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, journalist
