 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-8::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
2 different pets are kept: dog, frog
1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi |
| Pet           | frog       | dog       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-9::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, electrician
House: tower, cottage
1. the tower house is in an even position##4
2. the electrician is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |
| Job           | doctor | electrician |
| House   | cottage | tower    |

