.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, corn
2 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is the person eating corn##1
2. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Food          | corn | blueberry |
| Game   | backgammon | monopoly   |

